<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MoneyMapper - Login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            background: #f8fafc;
            color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
            /* Prevent body from scrolling on desktop */
        }

        /* Left Panel - Login Form */
        .login-panel {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1.5rem 5%;
            /* Reduced padding for compactness */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #fff;
            overflow-y: hidden;
            /* Hide overflow to remove scrollbar */
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            /* Reduced font size */
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            /* Reduced margin */
        }

        .welcome-text h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            /* Reduced font size */
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .welcome-text p {
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            /* Reduced margin */
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            /* Reduced margin */
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #334155;
        }

        input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            /* Reduced padding */
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #2563eb;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
        }

        .remember-forgot {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            /* Reduced margin */
        }

        .remember {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .remember input {
            width: auto;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .remember label {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .forgot-password {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .forgot-password:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .login-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.9rem;
            /* Reduced padding */
            background: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .login-btn:hover {
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }

        .divider {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 1.25rem 0;
            /* Reduced margin */
            position: relative;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .divider::before,
        .divider::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            width: 42%;
            height: 1px;
            background: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .divider::before {
            left: 0;
        }

        .divider::after {
            right: 0;
        }

        .social-login {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            /* Reduced margin */
        }

        .social-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 0.8rem;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .social-btn.google {
            color: #3f3f3f;
        }

        .social-btn.apple {
            color: #000000;
        }

        .social-btn:hover {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .register-link {
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .register-link a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .register-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            /* Reduced margin */
            text-align: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .copyright p {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .copyright a {
            color: #64748b;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .copyright a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Right Panel - Feature Showcase */
        .feature-panel {
            flex: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d2a4a 0%, #1a365d 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 5%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow-y: auto;
            /* Allow internal scrolling on this panel */
        }

        .feature-content {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .feature-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .feature-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #cbd5e1;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .stat-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            body {
                flex-direction: column;
                height: auto;
                /* Allow body to grow on mobile */
                overflow-y: auto;
                /* Allow normal page scrolling on mobile */
            }

            .login-panel,
            .feature-panel {
                overflow-y: visible;
                /* Disable internal scrolling on mobile */
                max-width: 100%;
                flex: 1 1 auto;
                /* Allow panels to size to content */
            }

            .feature-panel {
                padding: 3rem 5%;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="login-panel">
        <div class="logo">MoneyMapper.</div>

        <div class="welcome-text">
            <h1>Welcome Back</h1>
            <p>Enter your email and password to access your account.</p>
        </div>

        <form>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" value="">
            </div>

            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="password">Password</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" value="">
            </div>

            <div class="remember-forgot">
                <div class="remember">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="remember">
                    <label for="remember">Remember Me</label>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="forgot-password">Forgot Password?</a>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="login-btn">Log in</button>
        </form>

        <div class="divider">Or Login With</div>

        <div class="social-login">
            <button class="social-btn google">
                <i class="fab fa-google"></i>
                Google
            </button>
            <button class="social-btn apple">
                <i class="fab fa-apple"></i>
                Apple
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="register-link">
            Don't Have An Account? <a href="/signup">Register Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="copyright">
            <p>Copyright Â© 2025 MoneyMapper.</p>
            <p><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-panel">
        <div class="feature-content">
            <h2>Effortlessly manage your rent and operations.</h2>
            <p>Log in to access your MoneyMapper dashboard and manage your rent, flat, houses.</p>

            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">19,374</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Active Users</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">26.8%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Monthly Growth</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">89,370</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Tasks Completed</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">9,340</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">New Leads</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">33.0%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Conversion Rate</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">8k+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Units Managed</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Simple form validation
        document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
            e.preventDefault();

            const email = document.getElementById('email').value;
            const password = document.getElementById('password').value;

            if (email && password) {
                // In a real application, you would send this to a server
                alert('Login successful! Redirecting to dashboard...');
                // window.location.href = 'dashboard.html';
            } else {
                alert('Please fill in both email and password fields.');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>